Class WorkgroupQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jivesoftware.smackx.workgroup.agent.WorkgroupQueue

  • public class WorkgroupQueue
extends Object
    A queue in a workgroup, which is a pool of agents that are routed a specific type of chat request.
